322
00:20:14,120 --> 00:20:15,120
Wan Xinxin.

323
00:20:17,200 --> 00:20:18,120
Wan Xinxin.

324
00:20:24,360 --> 00:20:24,880
How is it?

325
00:20:24,880 --> 00:20:25,640
What do you mean?

326
00:20:25,640 --> 00:20:26,920
