332
00:20:38,360 --> 00:20:39,800
No, in this place you're really...

333
00:20:39,800 --> 00:20:40,760
You're really...

334
00:20:40,760 --> 00:20:43,560
If someone sees me putting my hand in there, they'll think...

335
00:20:43,560 --> 00:20:46,520
Weren't you brave enough last night?

336
00:20:46,960 --> 00:20:49,090
Last night I was drunk. That's enough.

337
00:20:51,320 --> 00:20:53,360
So it was the alcohol that made you so forward?

338
00:20:53,360 --> 00:20:55,360
Alcohol gives courage to the timid.

339
00:20:57,320 --> 00:20:58,640
Do you love me or not?

340
00:20:59,080 --> 00:21:01,280
