341
00:21:01,280 --> 00:21:01,800
Yes.

342
00:21:01,960 --> 00:21:02,880
You really want to discuss this here?

343
00:21:02,880 --> 00:21:03,680
Yes.

344
00:21:06,320 --> 00:21:07,840
You really want to talk about it here?

345
00:21:07,840 --> 00:21:09,520
Fine then. Let's talk about it right here.

346
00:21:09,520 --> 00:21:10,440
Wait, what are you doing?

347
00:21:10,440 --> 00:21:10,960
What am I doing?

348
00:21:10,960 --> 00:21:12,840
What do you mean? Why are you backing out now?

349
00:21:12,840 --> 00:21:13,760
You were just acting all confident.

350
00:21:13,760 --> 00:21:14,720
Come on.

351
00:21:17,400 --> 00:21:19,440
Okay, okay. Phone, phone.

352
00:21:24,680 --> 00:21:25,800
Hello?

353
00:21:29,200 --> 00:21:31,200
Wait for me. I'll be right there.

354
00:21:32,080 --> 00:21:33,080
What's wrong?

355
00:21:33,480 --> 00:21:34,640
There's a critical patient at the hospital.

356
00:21:34,640 --> 00:21:36,280
