372
00:22:31,560 --> 00:22:33,240
Why do I do it? For this family.

373
00:22:33,680 --> 00:22:34,520
But

374
00:22:35,680 --> 00:22:36,640
I got fired.

375
00:22:38,800 --> 00:22:40,360
Qin Gang has gone too far.

376
00:22:40,480 --> 00:22:42,200
