408
00:24:17,400 --> 00:24:19,000
If we don't separate, neither of us will be okay.

409
00:24:19,000 --> 00:24:21,440
You and your sister are the bane of my existence.

410
00:24:21,440 --> 00:24:22,800
It's not like that.

411
00:24:22,960 --> 00:24:24,520
Haven't I told you before?

412
00:24:24,840 --> 00:24:27,120
Qin Gang just wants the child to fight for the family inheritance.

413
00:24:27,120 --> 00:24:29,240
