418
00:24:40,840 --> 00:24:42,280
He'll marry Liu Wei.

419
00:24:42,800 --> 00:24:44,360
So you're saying Liu Wei...

420
00:24:44,480 --> 00:24:47,080
If she helps Qin Gang get the child,

421
00:24:47,160 --> 00:24:49,560
then she won't cause any more trouble?

422
00:24:50,840 --> 00:24:52,840
