438
00:26:07,040 --> 00:26:08,500
I can't help you with that.

439
00:26:08,560 --> 00:26:10,420
I'm not the manager of this store.

440
00:26:10,440 --> 00:26:11,320
Mr. Liu.

441
00:26:11,800 --> 00:26:15,200
Look, I'm Wan Xinxin's brother-in-law.

442
00:26:15,640 --> 00:26:19,080
It's like this. From what I understand, you want

443
00:26:19,760 --> 00:26:21,400
to have a child, right?

444
00:26:21,760 --> 00:26:23,440
I think I can help with that.

445
00:26:23,560 --> 00:26:25,720
If Mr. Qin gets custody of the child, wouldn't

446
00:26:25,720 --> 00:26:27,520
