447
00:26:27,520 --> 00:26:29,000
Who told you all this?

448
00:26:29,120 --> 00:26:30,680
It's completely untrue.

449
00:26:30,840 --> 00:26:31,880
And also,

450
00:26:32,120 --> 00:26:34,760
I'm warning you. Don't harass me again.

451
00:26:35,040 --> 00:26:36,360
How annoying!

452
00:27:03,800 --> 00:27:04,520
Xinxin.

453
00:27:04,640 --> 00:27:07,370
It's fine if I made too much and we can't finish it.

454
00:27:09,000 --> 00:27:10,080
What are you doing?

455
00:27:10,760 --> 00:27:12,400
Aren't you very busy?

456
00:27:14,000 --> 00:27:15,000
Yes.

457
00:27:15,000 --> 00:27:16,840
I really wasn't running away, Xinxin.

458
00:27:16,840 --> 00:27:19,120
The project situation was quite complicated.

459
00:27:19,120 --> 00:27:19,800
And also,

460
00:27:19,800 --> 00:27:22,120
there was a real emergency at the hospital. I had to leave.

461
00:27:22,120 --> 00:27:24,960
I understand. I really do.

462
00:27:25,120 --> 00:27:26,200
It's a matter of life and death.

463
00:27:26,200 --> 00:27:27,880
I'm not that unreasonable.

464
00:27:28,760 --> 00:27:29,640
Let me tell you,

465
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:32,000
you're warm inside and out,

466
00:27:32,080 --> 00:27:33,240
like a little sun, so understanding.

467
00:27:33,240 --> 00:27:34,760
That's exactly the kind of girl you are.

468
00:27:34,760 --> 00:27:36,600
Enough. Stop flattering me.

469
00:27:36,680 --> 00:27:38,810
I don't want to be that understanding.

470
00:27:40,200 --> 00:27:41,200
Really, Xinxin,

471
00:27:41,200 --> 00:27:42,640
I'm really in a hurry here.

472
00:27:42,640 --> 00:27:44,480
I need to prepare several plans.

473
00:27:44,880 --> 00:27:46,080
No, no.

474
00:27:47,920 --> 00:27:48,760
I finally understand

475
00:27:48,760 --> 00:27:50,640
