476
00:27:50,760 --> 00:27:52,080
When you fall in love with someone,

477
00:27:52,080 --> 00:27:53,640
you have to fall into the dust.

478
00:27:53,640 --> 00:27:55,360
Yes, I admit it.

479
00:27:56,280 --> 00:27:58,800
