481
00:28:02,320 --> 00:28:03,200
Xinxin.

482
00:28:03,200 --> 00:28:04,530
Go ahead with your work.

483
00:28:46,680 --> 00:28:47,600
Huaming.

484
00:28:47,760 --> 00:28:48,960
Senior, how did it go?

485
00:28:49,120 --> 00:28:50,000
No problem.

486
00:28:50,240 --> 00:28:52,120
The interventional surgery was very successful.

487
00:28:52,120 --> 00:28:54,400
