488
00:28:54,680 --> 00:28:55,800
A master is always a master.

489
00:28:55,800 --> 00:28:57,560
Huaming, I'm impressed.

490
00:28:57,840 --> 00:28:58,920
That's good.

491
00:29:00,280 --> 00:29:03,480
I believe you'll always overcome difficulties.

492
00:29:03,640 --> 00:29:06,040
In the future, the position of lead surgeon

493
00:29:06,120 --> 00:29:07,580
will definitely be yours.

494
00:29:07,600 --> 00:29:09,440
No one can surpass you.

495
00:29:34,160 --> 00:29:37,440
I'm telling you, I'm always so happy to see you.

496
00:29:37,440 --> 00:29:39,570
Does that make me seem materialistic?

497
00:29:39,760 --> 00:29:42,200
As an artist, if you talk like that,

498
00:29:42,320 --> 00:29:43,850
