522
00:30:36,800 --> 00:30:38,040
I need to get home right away.

523
00:30:38,040 --> 00:30:39,640
If there are no customers, just close the shop.

524
00:30:39,640 --> 00:30:40,840
Thank you. Thank you.

525
00:30:46,000 --> 00:30:47,120
Let's go, darling.

526
00:30:47,280 --> 00:30:48,240
I'll go first then.

527
00:30:48,240 --> 00:30:49,040
Go ahead. Go ahead.

528
00:30:49,040 --> 00:30:50,000
Bye-bye.

529
00:30:50,440 --> 00:30:51,720
Don't worry.

530
00:30:52,480 --> 00:30:54,360
