559
00:32:48,480 --> 00:32:49,810
I know you believe in me,

560
00:32:50,080 --> 00:32:52,200
but I don't believe in myself.

561
00:32:53,480 --> 00:32:55,040
I'm like a chef

562
00:32:55,160 --> 00:32:56,400
