00:33:19,760 --> 00:33:20,880
in my heart,

569
00:33:21,320 --> 00:33:22,960
you're always the best.

570
00:33:23,720 --> 00:33:25,640
You're just like my darling now,

571
00:33:26,080 --> 00:33:29,680
both of you are the most important to me.

572
00:33:31,480 --> 00:33:32,720
The thing is,

573
00:33:34,040 --> 00:33:36,320
I love you so much.

574
00:34:37,120 --> 00:34:38,040
What are you doing?

575
00:34:38,040 --> 00:34:39,370
I need to take this call.

576
00:34:41,000 --> 00:34:41,920
Hello?

577
00:34:44,719 --> 00:34:45,840
You're back.

578
00:34:50,800 --> 00:34:52,760
Xinxin.

579
00:34:53,360 --> 00:34:54,360
Xinxin.

580
00:34:55,120 --> 00:34:56,159
What's wrong now?

581
