591
00:35:27,320 --> 00:35:29,880
You're divorced from your ex-wife, aren't you?

592
00:35:29,880 --> 00:35:30,480
So am I now

593
00:35:30,600 --> 00:35:32,680
your legitimate girlfriend?

594
00:35:32,800 --> 00:35:33,640
Yes.

595
00:35:34,320 --> 00:35:36,400
