596
00:35:36,400 --> 00:35:37,800
Making me feel like I'm the other woman.

597
00:35:37,800 --> 00:35:39,600
No, why would you say something so harsh?

598
00:35:39,600 --> 00:35:41,600
Xia Qing actually has

599
