a boyfriend in America and they were about to get married.

600
00:35:44,720 --> 00:35:46,600
But Ruirui ruined it.

601
00:35:46,720 --> 00:35:48,640
You don't want our relationship

602
00:35:49,240 --> 00:35:51,170
to be killed in its infancy, do you?

603
00:35:51,320 --> 00:35:52,360
Your daughter...

604
00:35:54,120 --> 00:35:55,800
Wait, the way you describe her,

605
00:35:55,800 --> 00:35:57,920
she sounds like a little demon.

606
00:36:00,760 --> 00:36:02,680
Well, let's do this.

607
00:36:03,200 --> 00:36:04,400
Try not to meet her.

608
00:36:04,520 --> 00:36:06,720
If you do meet, follow my lead.

609
00:36:07,640 --> 00:36:09,370
So treat me like I'm invisible?

610
00:36:09,640 --> 00:36:11,120
Keep me silent, right?

611
00:36:11,720 --> 00:36:13,320
Silence is golden.

612
00:36:13,320 --> 00:36:15,080
Come on, let me tell you.

613
00:36:15,400 --> 00:36:18,320
If I don't explode in silence, I'll perish in silence.

614
00:36:18,320 --> 00:36:19,680
You'll be in trouble.

615
00:36:22,120 --> 00:36:23,720
Yes, I'll be in trouble.

616
00:36:23,840 --> 00:36:26,120
Because you're like a big pancake wrap.

617
00:36:26,240 --> 00:36:28,600
You're my most delicious pancake wrap.

618
00:36:28,840 --> 00:36:30,480
Before I finish this pancake,

619
00:36:30,480 --> 00:36:32,240
I need to make you Mrs. Hua.

620
00:36:33,080 --> 00:36:34,440
Dream on.

621
00:36:37,400 --> 00:36:38,730
Don't be angry anymore.

622
00:36:39,000 --> 00:36:40,660
Well, I'll go pick them up now.

623
00:36:43,280 --> 00:36:44,480
They don't live here.

624
00:36:44,560 --> 00:36:45,920
What are you talking about? How could they stay here?

625
00:36:45,920 --> 00:36:46,880
This place is for us.

626
00:36:46,880 --> 00:36:48,010
I've booked a hotel.

627
00:36:49,000 --> 00:36:50,680
At least you have some conscience.

628
00:36:50,680 --> 00:36:51,640
Let's go.

629
00:36:54,480 --> 00:36:55,600
Tell me now.

630
00:36:55,840 --> 00:36:57,080
What am I to you?

631
00:36:59,840 --> 00:37:00,840
Come closer.

632
00:37:02,240 --> 00:37:03,120
Friend.

633
00:37:03,840 --> 00:37:04,800
What?

634
00:37:05,320 --> 00:37:06,520
Girlfriend.

635
00:37:06,920 --> 00:37:08,240
That's more like it.

636
00:37:08,400 --> 00:37:09,280
Muah.

637
00:37:09,920 --> 00:37:10,880
Let's go.

638
00:37:17,920 --> 00:37:18,840
What are you

639
00:37:19,600 --> 00:37:21,160
doing?

640
00:37:21,640 --> 00:37:22,640
What do you think?

641
00:37:28,640 --> 00:37:30,700
I'm changing clothes to pick them up.

642
00:37:43,320 --> 00:37:46,440
Attention all those meeting passengers.

643
00:37:46,840 --> 00:37:49,920
Flights from New York, San Francisco and Shanghai

644
00:37:49,920 --> 00:37:51,120
arriving in Beijing.

645
00:37:52,200 --> 00:37:53,040
Hey.

646
00:37:53,640 --> 00:37:56,000
I'm at the parking lot. Where are you?

647
00:37:57,840 --> 00:37:58,840
Put your hands up.

648
00:38:01,240 --> 00:38:03,400
Okay.

649
00:38:03,520 --> 00:38:04,800
Turn around.

650
00:38:06,160 --> 00:38:07,080
Slowly.

651
00:38:07,120 --> 00:38:08,520
Okay.

652
00:38:08,560 --> 00:38:10,760
Slowly.

653
00:38:10,760 --> 00:38:11,800
Okay.

654
00:38:14,400 --> 00:38:15,520
Alright.

655
00:38:19,800 --> 00:38:20,530
Sweetheart.

656
00:38:20,560 --> 00:38:23,640
Daddy, you should lie down like a mermaid.

657
00:38:24,960 --> 00:38:26,120
I love you.

658
00:38:26,440 --> 00:38:27,960
Daddy.

659
00:38:28,160 --> 00:38:30,360
Daddy.

660
00:38:31,240 --> 00:38:32,320
Daddy.

661
00:38:34,640 --> 00:38:36,960
Daddy, I missed you.

662
00:38:37,560 --> 00:38:38,920
I missed you too.

663
00:38:39,200 --> 00:38:39,760
I missed you so much.

664
00:38:39,760 --> 00:38:40,480
Daddy,

665
00:38:41,000 --> 00:38:42,160
Mom is over there.

666
00:38:56,000 --> 00:38:57,160
Mom.

667
00:39:00,960 --> 00:39:01,960
Long time no see.

668
00:39:02,720 --> 00:39:05,050
You're looking more energetic than ever.

669
00:39:07,680 --> 00:39:09,680
Men and women are just different.

670
00:39:10,120 --> 00:39:11,760
Men bloom at forty,

671
00:39:11,880 --> 00:39:12,880
unlike women,

672
00:39:13,040 --> 00:39:15,000
who go downhill after thirty.

673
00:39:15,440 --> 00:39:17,600
Your dad is in his prime now.

674
00:39:18,640 --> 00:39:20,640
Must have lots of girls chasing him.

675
00:39:23,440 --> 00:39:25,370
Daddy, you can't date anyone else.

676
00:39:25,480 --> 00:39:27,210
Besides, Mom and I are back now.

677
00:39:27,360 --> 00:39:29,220
So we should be together forever,

678
00:39:29,320 --> 00:39:30,560
okay?

679
00:39:32,960 --> 00:39:34,840
Good. Ruirui, from now on,

680
00:39:34,960 --> 00:39:36,280
we'll always stay with Daddy, okay?

681
00:39:36,280 --> 00:39:37,440
Okay.

682
00:39:43,520 --> 00:39:45,360
Ruirui, watch out for cars.

683
00:39:48,400 --> 00:39:50,200
Tell me about your girlfriend.

684
00:39:52,440 --> 00:39:54,440
You still think you can hide it from me?

685
00:39:54,440 --> 00:39:55,240
After all these years,

686
00:39:55,240 --> 00:39:57,360
nothing escapes my eyes.

687
00:40:01,400 --> 00:40:03,360
The moment I saw you at the airport,

688
00:40:04,000 --> 00:40:06,000
