689
00:40:07,880 --> 00:40:11,140
You didn't tell me because you were afraid I'd mind, right?

690
00:40:13,520 --> 00:40:15,180
It's because Ruirui was here.

691
00:40:20,920 --> 00:40:22,780
Do you still have feelings for me?

692
00:40:26,720 --> 00:40:27,560
Xia Qing.

693
00:40:28,600 --> 00:40:30,760
When you left with Ruirui back then,

694
00:40:31,000 --> 00:40:32,880
I think we made everything clear.

695
00:40:33,240 --> 00:40:34,200
So now,

696
00:40:34,320 --> 00:40:36,920
I don't need to explain anything to you, right?

697
00:40:51,480 --> 00:40:54,840
Has your hand not recovered yet?

698
00:40:57,000 --> 00:40:58,600
Let's go. Ruirui is waiting.

699
00:41:15,080 --> 00:41:16,280
We're here.

700
