You little piggy, you've gotten so heavy now.

701
00:41:27,200 --> 00:41:28,400
We'll stay here.

702
00:41:28,520 --> 00:41:30,200
Please take our luggage to room 1201.

703
00:41:30,200 --> 00:41:31,000
Sure.

704
00:41:34,800 --> 00:41:37,520
Dad, we haven't been home for years.

705
00:41:37,520 --> 00:41:40,200
And you're making me stay in this cold hotel?

706
00:41:41,640 --> 00:41:42,520
Is this hotel cold?

707
00:41:42,520 --> 00:41:44,400
This is a very upscale hotel, okay?

708
00:41:44,400 --> 00:41:45,440
Don't you want to stay in a suite?

709
00:41:45,440 --> 00:41:47,360
Dad booked a really beautiful suite.

710
00:41:47,360 --> 00:41:48,360
The benefits of staying in a hotel:

711
00:41:48,360 --> 00:41:49,720
First, you don't have to clean up yourself.

712
00:41:49,720 --> 00:41:50,880
Second, whatever food you want,

713
00:41:50,880 --> 00:41:52,800
