714
00:41:52,800 --> 00:41:54,760
But I want to eat what my dad cooks.

715
00:41:56,040 --> 00:41:57,700
Did you really sell the house?

716
00:42:01,160 --> 00:42:02,440
You said you were selling the house

717
00:42:02,440 --> 00:42:04,000
to come find us in America.

718
00:42:05,240 --> 00:42:06,280
Didn't you say

719
00:42:06,280 --> 00:42:09,140
you were going to get your medical license in the US?

720
00:42:09,960 --> 00:42:12,820
Dad has some things he can't get away from right now.

721
00:42:13,520 --> 00:42:14,280
If you can't get away,

722
00:42:14,280 --> 00:42:16,340
then I should stay with you even more.

723
00:42:16,480 --> 00:42:18,560
Dad, please take me and mom home.

724
00:42:18,560 --> 00:42:21,420
We can cook for you together. Wouldn't that be nice?

725
00:42:22,960 --> 00:42:24,420
Let's listen to our child.

726
00:42:24,680 --> 00:42:26,810
I don't like staying in hotels either.

727
00:42:28,080 --> 00:42:31,040
Right now, there's nowhere for us to go back to.

728
00:42:31,480 --> 00:42:32,880
Where are you living now?

729
00:42:37,040 --> 00:42:37,840
An apartment.

730
00:43:48,360 --> 00:43:49,090
Wang Yaping.

731
00:43:49,480 --> 00:43:50,140
Li Wengang.

732
00:43:50,240 --> 00:43:50,770
Qiaohua.

733
00:44:12,280 --> 00:44:12,640
(Yeng Yun)

